name: You Swindled Me! (V)
Lore: 'Needless to say, Watto was not happy about his loss.',
Text: 'USED: Reveal the top four cards of your Reserve Deck and separate them into two piles of any size. Opponent places one pile in your hand and the other on top of your Used Pile in any order. OR take into hand Alter from Reserve Deck; reshuffle. LOST: Place an opponent''s just-played Interrupt out of play.',
